_meanings:
Following in death;  
{#tanmaraRe cAnumaraRaM karizyAmIti me niScayaH#} <ls>H. 3</ls>;
post-cremation of a widow ({#anumaraRaM#}
{#hi BarturdeSAMtarAdimaraRe dehAdyalABa eva#}); 
{#deSAMtaramfte patyO sADvI tatpAdukAdvayaM . niDAyorasi#}
{#saMSudDA praviSejjAtavedasaM ..#} This is allowed
to Kṣatriya, Vaiśya and other
women, but not to Brāhmaṇa women;
{#pfTak citAM samAruhya na viprA gaMtumarhati#}. Bāṇa
severely condemns this practice; see
<ls>K. 173-4</ls>.
